### Update Course (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/course/admin/69258bc54a4b6921ecababdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CourseFormBoundaryUpdate

------CourseFormBoundaryUpdate
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Updated Course Title
------CourseFormBoundaryUpdate
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="remove_gallery"

["https://cloudinary.com/image/old1.jpg"]
------CourseFormBoundaryUpdate
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="keep_gallery"

["https://cloudinary.com/image/keep1.jpg"]
------CourseFormBoundaryUpdate
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="thumbnail"; filename="updated-thumb.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-media/test.png
------CourseFormBoundaryUpdate--

